*Pokušaću* da se probudim što ranije ujutru. (I will try to wake up as early as possible in the morning.)

Želim da *pokušam* da napravim novi recept. (I want to try to make a new recipe.)

Šta ako *pokušam* da promenim svoj stav? (What if I try to change my attitude?)

Nemam puno vremena, ali ću *pokušati* da stignem. (I don't have much time, but I'll try to make it.)

*Pokušaću* da izdržim do kraja. (I'll try to last until the end.)